        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p07-prepare: Assemble data analytics source packet; Collect the source material needed for data analytics.; aliases=['gather data analytics inputs', 'prepare data analytics packet']\n- v07-p07-verify: Validate data analytics source packet; Check the assembled data analytics material for correctness.; aliases=['check data analytics inputs', 'verify data analytics packet']\n- v07-p07-deliver: Publish data analytics verified brief; Release the checked final brief for data analytics.; aliases=['issue data analytics brief', 'release data analytics summary']\n- v07-p07-archive: Archive data analytics verified brief; Preserve the checked data analytics brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain data analytics brief', 'store data analytics summary']\n- v07-p07-distractor-1: Auxiliary data analytics operation 1; Perform unrelated data analytics auxiliary operation number 1.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p07 1']\n- v07-p07-distractor-2: Auxiliary data analytics operation 2; Perform unrelated data analytics auxiliary operation number 2.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p07 2']\n- v07-p07-distractor-3: Auxiliary data analytics operation 3; Perform unrelated data analytics auxiliary operation number 3.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p07 3']\n- v07-p07-distractor-4: Auxiliary data analytics operation 4; Perform unrelated data analytics auxiliary operation number 4.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p07 4']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p07-ordinary: ordinary data analytics assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this data analytics request.; aliases=['normal data analytics assurance']\n- v07-p07-elevated: elevated data analytics assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this data analytics request.; aliases=['high assurance for data analytics']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p07-json: data analytics machine-readable JSON; Return the final data analytics result as JSON.; aliases=['data analytics json output']\n- v07-p07-signed-pdf: data analytics signed PDF; Return the final data analytics result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed data analytics document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p07-preparer: data analytics source preparer\n- v07-p07-verifier: data analytics source verifier\n- v07-p07-primary: primary data analytics publisher\n- v07-p07-backup: backup data analytics publisher\n\nREQUEST\nFor this data analytics job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal data analytics assurance as data analytics JSON output. Do not use the primary data analytics publisher or the backup data analytics publisher."
